Personal Data Collection: We may collect personal data such as your name, email address, and other information you provide during the registration or profile creation process. Additionally, we may collect technical information about your device and usage patterns, including IP address, browser type, and app interactions.

Data Usage: We use the collected data to facilitate your video conferencing experience, authenticate users, establish connections between participants, and provide app features and services. We may also analyze usage patterns to improve app functionality, troubleshoot issues, and personalize your experience.

Data Sharing: We do not sell, rent, or lease your personal data to third parties. However, we may share your information with trusted service providers who assist us in delivering our services, subject to strict confidentiality agreements. We may also disclose data to comply with legal obligations or protect our rights and safety.

Data Access and Processing: Access to your personal data is limited to authorized personnel who need it for app maintenance, support, or system administration purposes. We implement security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, loss, or alteration. Your data may be processed and stored in locations outside your country of residence.

Privacy Rights and Choices: You have the right to access, update, and delete your personal data. You can manage your privacy settings within the app, including opting out of certain data processing activities. You may also unsubscribe from marketing communications. We respect your choices and will respond to your requests promptly.

Children: Our app is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children. If we become aware of any such data, we will take immediate steps to delete it from our systems.

Third-Party Links: Our app may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these sites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies before interacting with them.

Changes to the Privacy Policy: We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any material changes will be notified to you through the app or other appropriate means. Please review the policy periodically to stay informed about how we handle your personal information.

Contact Us: If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding your personal data or this Privacy Policy, please contact us using the information provided in the app.

This Privacy Policy is effective as of [Effective Date] and governs the use of your personal data in connection with the Huddle Up app. By using our app, you consent to the collection, use, and sharing of your personal information as described in this policy.
